  "data_caveat": "Single source (theoddsapi), 72 matches over ~12 days, one-3-way-market (h2h). Estimators restricted to a fixed 16-book panel for a fair comparison. The 'close' is the last snapshot at/before kickoff, but capture cadence usually stopped early: only 8/72 matches have a snapshot within 60 min of kickoff (median gap ~38.0h), so the de-vigged close is a best-available pre-KO line, not a true settle. TEST 1 (predict close) is full-n but indicative; TEST 2 (predict result) has n=31 => indicative, not significant. No Polymarket price history exists; this is sportsbook+exchange consensus only."
